	directAnswerHtml={`<strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">If you're walking through separation or divorce, the Father's Heart Bible™ is for you.</strong> You carry more than people see — the grief, the rejection, the shame, the fear of a future you didn't plan. The <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Father's Heart Bible™</a> is a fresh English translation you can read and <em>listen to</em> free on your phone — and it reveals God as a <em>Father</em> from beginning to end. Whether you searched "Bible verses for divorce," "verses for separation," "comfort after heartbreak," or "starting over" — the answer is not condemnation or a scarlet letter. Even when a covenant has been broken, the Father's covenant with you is not. He stays close to the brokenhearted, and He will never leave you.`}
