		{ question: `Is there a free Bible with audio for comfort during divorce?`, answer: `Yes. The Father's Heart Bible™ is free to read and listen to online — no account, no purchase, no app. Open fathersheartbible.com/read on your phone and read or hear any book — perfect for the quiet nights, the long drives, or whenever the grief feels heaviest.` },
